Title: Blood Money
Description: Andy Warburton is kidnapped by two of his friends and Tony is asked to bring the ransom. It was all a joke, but as Tony arrives, he finds out that Andy is kidnapped again - this time for real.
Short Description: Tony is caught in the middle of a kidnapping for ransom.

Title: Any Number Can Die
Description: Paul asks his old friend Tony to make him a testament and an envelope addressed to Frank Keegan for storage. Later Paul dies in an explosion and Keegan also dies in an accident. Tony tries to find out who is responsible for his friend's death.
Short Description: Tony tries to find out who is responsible for his friend's death.

Title: Deadly Journey
Description: An elderly lady needs Petrocelli's help when she's accused of killing the car dealer who fired her son from his job at the dealership.
Short Description: Petrocelli helps a mother accused of murder to help her son.

Title: Jubilee Jones
Description: Tony represents an entertainer who's charged with killing the manager of the club where he works.
Short Description: Tony represents an entertainer accused of murder.

Title: The Night Visitor
Description: A mysterious man leaves an envelope in Petrocelli's office for storage, but later he disappears and somebody is capable of everything to have that envelope.
Short Description: A mysterious envelope is pursued at the cost of a life.

Title: To See No Evil
Description: A young blind woman is accused of killing an intruder.
Short Description: A young blind woman is accused of killing an intruder.

Title: The Gamblers
Description: A pizzeria owner is found dead by his employee Mando Rivera, who in panic runs away but is seen by the victim's friends so Mando is arrested for murder.
Short Description: Mando is accused of killing his boss.

Title: Terror on Wheels
Description: Dimitri is accused of killing Nick.
Short Description: Dimitri is accused of killing Nick.

Title: Face of Evil
Description: Petrocelli is hired by Mary Wade to help her twin Janet in a murder case. Janet has huge blackout about that night, Mary also disappears, that all makes Tony's job of finding the truth very difficult.
Short Description: Petrocelli is hired by Mary Wade to help her twin Janet in a murder case.

Title: Too Many Alibis
Description: Petrocelli's client is a conscientious black doctor accused of killing the hospital chief of staff, who charged him with incompetence and fired him.
Short Description: A Black doctor is accused of killing the hospital chief of staff.

Title: Survival
Description: Don Janssen is arrested for robbery, but escaped to Mexico. When brought back from Mexico in a police car along with Petrocelli, they are attacked and chased in the Mexican desert by the men who want their robbed values back.
Short Description: Don Janssen is arrested for robbery and needs help from Petrocelli.

Title: Four the Hard Way
Description: Ex-cowboy Clate Dobie is wanted for murder, but his three friends hire Petrocelli help him.
Short Description: Ex-cowboy Clate Dobie is wanted for murder, but his three friends hire Petrocelli help him.

Title: Shadow of Fear
Description: Petrocelli's client thinks she killed her ex-husband, only to find out differently.
Short Description: Petrocelli's client thinks she killed her ex-husband, only to find out differently.

Title: Death Ride
Description: Rodeo clown Gage seems to have murdered a rival rodeo man.
Short Description: Rodeo clown Gage seems to have murdered a rival rodeo man.

Title: Five Yards of Trouble
Description: Charlie is accused of killing Mr. Woodward.
Short Description: Charlie is accused of killing Mr. Woodward.

Title: A Lonely Victim
Description: Mary Thorpe is accused of murdering her married lover, Raymond Walker after an argument about their affair.
Short Description: Mary Thorpe is accused of murdering her married lover, Raymond Walker after an argument about their affair.

Title: The Sleep of Reason
Description: A student who was having a dispute with a professor walks into a lecture the man is giving, pulls out a gun and shoots him. When questioned, he doesn't remember anything.
Short Description: A student shoots his teacher and loses memory of the incident.
